{"id": "unknown-2026-04-29-034", "date": "2026-04-29", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 18, "weekday": "Wed"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "Researcher design a high-performance asymmetric MR-TADF deep-blue OLED emitter", "content": "<p>Researchers from Tsinghua University and Taiyuan University of Technology developed a novel asymmetric MR-TADF deep-blue OLED emitter structure design, that offers high efficiency and narrow-band emission.</p><div>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/2026-04/Asymmetric-oriented-deep-blue-high-EQE-MR-TADF.png\" target=\"_blank\">\n    \n    <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/2026-04/Asymmetric-oriented-deep-blue-high-EQ", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/researcher-design-high-performance-asymmetric-mr-tadf-deep-blue-oled-emitter", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "lg_display-2026-04-29-035", "date": "2026-04-29", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 18, "weekday": "Wed"}, "entities": {"companies": ["lg_display"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["panel_price", "oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.5, "keywords": ["increase"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "KDIA: Korean OLED market share has risen 1.5% in 2025, for the first time since 2015", "content": "<p>The Korean Display Industry Association (KDIA) is quoting Omdia, saying that the OLED market share of Korean OLED panels (made by LGD and SDC) have increased 1.5% in 2025, to reach 68.7%. This is the first time since 2015 that Korea's OLED market share has increased.&nbsp;</p><div>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/2026-04/Korea-vs-China-OLED-share-KDIA-Omdia.png\" target=\"_blank\">\n    \n    <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/styles/", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/kdia-korean-oled-market-share-has-risen-15-2025-first-time-2015", "type": "rss"}]}
